The idea of a pop star traveling to the final frontier was wild enough on its own for the internet to go crazy over the mission, but Perry unveiling her Lifetimes Tour setlist in zero gravity and dramatically kissing the ground once she landed also fueled many posts and memes for weeks after the fact.

