â€œI was actually shocked, because I think between me and my friends and my family and the people that I always share my music and my art with first, it just wasnâ€™t even a conversation,â€ she later told CBS Mornings of the backlash. â€œFor what the album is, [the cover is] perfect for what it represents, and everything about it to me just felt so opposite of, like, the world ending.â€

